# Initially, its value is the empty string.
# The other properties are set to defaults.
run observe=(value,props,pos)
----
-- value:
""
-- props:
Focused: false
Width: 35, Height: 6, LogicalHeight: 1
Length: 0, LineCount: 1, NumLinesInValue: 1, EmptyValue: true
-- pos:
